\c 4
\s Ukubulawa kukaIshiboshethi
\p
\v 1 Lapho isizwile indodana kaSawuli ukuthi uAbhineri ufele eHebroni, izandla zakhe zaba buthakathaka, loIsrayeli wonke wakhathazeka\x + Ezra 4.4. Isa. 13.7. Jer. 6.24.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo indodana kaSawuli yayilamadoda amabili \add ayeyi\add*zinduna zamaviyo; ibizo lenye lalinguBahana, lebizo lenye linguRekabi, amadodana kaRimoni, umBherothi, wabantwana bakoBhenjamini\x + 23.37. Josh. 18.25.\x*. Ngoba iBherothi layo yayibalelwa koBhenjamini;
\v 3 lamaBherothi abalekela\x + 1 Sam. 31.7.\x* eGithayimi\x + 6.10,11. Neh. 11.33.\x*, aba ngabahlali njengabezizwe khona kuze kube lamuhla.
\p
\v 4 UJonathani indodana kaSawuli wayelendodana eyayiyisilima enyaweni\x + 9.3.\x*. Yayileminyaka emihlanu ekufikeni kombiko ngoSawuli loJonathani uvela eJizereyeli\x + 1 Sam. 29.1,11.\x*; lomlizane wayo wayithatha, wabaleka; kwasekusithi ekuphangiseni kwakhe ukubaleka, yawa yaba yisilima. Lebizo layo lalinguMefiboshethi.
\v 5 Lamadodana kaRimoni, umBherothi, uRekabi loBahana, ahamba, ekutshiseni kwelanga afika endlini kaIshiboshethi, owayelele embhedeni emini enkulu.
\v 6 Bona bangena endlini phakathi \add kungathi\add* bathatha ingqoloyi, bamtshaya kubambo lwesihlanu\x + 2.23.\x*; uRekabi loBahana umfowabo basebebaleka.
\v 7 Ngoba bengena endlini, wayelele embhedeni wakhe endlini yakhe yokulala, bamtshaya, bambulala, bamquma ikhanda; bathatha ikhanda lakhe, bahamba ngendlela yamagceke ubusuku bonke\x + 2.29.\x*.
\v 8 Basebelisa ikhanda likaIshiboshethi kuDavida eHebroni. Bathi enkosini: Khangela, ikhanda likaIshiboshethi indodana kaSawuli, isitha sakho ebesidinga impilo yakho; iN\nd kosi\nd* inike impindiselo lamuhla enkosini yami, inkosi, kuSawuli lakuyo inzalo yakhe\x + 1 Sam. 19.2,10,11. 23.15. 25.29.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Kodwa uDavida wabaphendula uRekabi loBahana umfowabo, amadodana kaRimoni umBherothi, wathi kubo: Kuphila kukaJehova\x + Ruthe 3.13.\x*, ohlenge umphefumulo wami kuyo yonke inhlupheko\x + 1 Kho. 1.29. Gen. 48.16. Hlab. 31.7.\x*,
\v 10 lapho owangibikelayo esithi: Khangela, uSawuli ufile; njalo enjengomthwali wendaba ezinhle emehlweni akhe, ngamxhakalaza, ngambulala eZikilagi, kulokuthi ngimvuzele indaba ezinhle\x + 1.2,4,15.\x*.
\v 11 Pho kangakanani, lapho abantu ababi bebulele umuntu olungileyo endlini yakhe esembhedeni wakhe; ngakho-ke angiyikubiza yini igazi lakhe esandleni senu, ngilisuse emhlabeni\x + Gen. 9.5,6.\x*?
\v 12 UDavida waselaya amajaha\x + Mark. 14.51.\x*, ababulala, aquma izandla zabo lenyawo zabo, abaphanyeka echibini leHebroni. Kodwa athatha ikhanda likaIshiboshethi, alingcwaba engcwabeni likaAbhineri eHebroni\x + 3.32.\x*.